---
import { APP_NAME, APP_TAGLINE } from "@kongsian/shared/constants";
---
<header class="container hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">For brand↔cafe partnerships in Indonesia</span>
  <h1>{APP_NAME}. <br/>{APP_TAGLINE}.</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    Konsinyasi untuk brand F&amp;B dan cafe. Catat Titip, jual harian, tutup minggu otomatis.
    Tanpa chat panjang. Tanpa spreadsheet. Tanpa drama akhir bulan.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-cta">
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#signup">Daftar via WhatsApp</a>
    <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#how">Cara kerja</a>
  </div>
  <p class="muted" style="font-size:13px;margin-top:24px">
    Week 1 build · monorepo: apps/web (Astro on Cloudflare Pages) + apps/api (Hono on Workers) + D1.
  </p>
</header>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 96px 24px 64px; }
  .hero h1 { color: var(--fg); }
  .hero h1 :global(br) + * { color: var(--brand); }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }
</style>
